'Other than general commands such as sit, lay down and paw etc, his first trick was to play dead which has become quite a crowd pleaser.

'It's impossible for me to choose a favourite trick - I think I'd have to say both his skateboarding trick and playing dead.' 

The street performer is also hoping Ziggy's impressive talents will help to disprove public stereotypes that Staffordshire bull terriers are a dangerous breed.

